      "id": 6,
      "title": "TraceQL Forensic Search Panel",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Forensic Incident Reconstruction\n\nTo find traces related to issues, go to **Explore** in Grafana and choose **Tempo**:\n\n* **Outages/Errors**: `{.error = true}`\n* **Slow Syncs (>15s)**: `{.sync.type = \"full\" && duration > 15s}`\n* **Redis Failures**: `{span.name =~ \"redis.command.*\" && .error = true}`\n* **DB Lock Contentions**: `{.anomaly.type = \"db_lock_contention\"}`\n* **Worker Replays**: `{span.name = \"worker.sync.execute\"}`"
      }
    }
